oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hotel located at Sam's Creek
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of a hotel located at Sam's Creek. The family of Isaac Franklin Bush (1836-1915) is standing outside the hotel. Harden Bush was a son of Isaac.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Hotels; Lodges; Families
